    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_fa5427b3">
            <lb />
            <head>
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName> WILL
                <lb />Play Again
            </head>
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#miracle" resp="#np" type="topic">
                Thanks to the wizardry of Hardman Welte-
                <lb />Mignon(licensee) Reproducing Pianos
            </seg>
            <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">
                the
                <lb />art of <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName> is imperishable
            </seg>.
            <seg ana="#repeatability" resp="#np" type="topic">
                He will
                <lb />play again, again and yet again for you -
                <lb />tonight, tomorrow night and other nights
            </seg>
            <lb />-
            <seg ana="#home" resp="#np" type="topic">
                in your own home.
            </seg>
            <lb /><persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">Hofmann</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116327642">Gabrilowitsch</persName>,
            <lb /><persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11875081X">Saint-Saens</persName> and the most celebrated pianists
            <lb />have expressed their conceptions of the
            <lb />world's classics on the Welte-Mignon.
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#c">
                Write for catalog.
                <lb />
